TopicTitle: Game doesn't load at home screen

Articles.Content:
Hi,

I am facing some problems with regards to loading my KSP. All files are loaded, but the home screen doesn't load. I understand that this problem was surfaced years back and was resolved. I have taken some actions on my behalf of trying to get the problem solved but to no avail. I hope you guys can help me out. Thx. Required files are attached below:

Picture of Problem: https://drive.google.com/file/d/16l9uusf9OQML84lAdTVol3GP5rH3rZOn/view?usp=sharing

Note: The game still runs and the loading bar moves. Bgm can be heard to.

Picture of game Data folder: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hcLJktHYuZwmGjaqDsjWQ4eBZ9UgkP5H/view?usp=sharing

KSP.log: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QCtfXJfkgtoSeDwqQK7_rQkAWPBFAL72/view?usp=sharing

 

Measures I have taken:

- Verified file integrity

- Reinstalled KSP after removing everything

- Removed all mods and ran KSP before adding all mods back and running it

- Removed certain mods that were said to cause problem

 

EDIT: The game data pic doesn't include RSS-Textures. It is also one of the mods I installed.
